# List of kings of Sigave

.]]
The King of Sigave (titled as Tu`i Sigave) is the ruler of the polity of Sigave, one of the two chiefdoms (Royaume coutumier, ) located on Futuna. Sigave encompasses the western part of the island.
Futuna is one of the Hoorn Islands in the French overseas collectivity of Wallis and Futuna.}}, in Oceania in the South Pacific Ocean.
